---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact" description="Get in touch with Roberto Carli for private wine tastings, corporate events, and consulting services in the Bay Area.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Let's Talk Wine</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-600 text-lg mb-12 max-w-2xl">Whether you're planning a private tasting, a corporate event, or simply want to learn more about wine, I'd love to hear from you.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <form class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-1">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-stone-300 px-4 py-3 text-stone-800 focus:border-amber-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-200 outline-none transition" placeholder="Your name" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-1">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-stone-300 px-4 py-3 text-stone-800 focus:border-amber-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-200 outline-none transition" placeholder="you@example.com" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="interest" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-1">I'm interested in</label>
            <select id="interest" name="interest" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-stone-300 px-4 py-3 text-stone-800 focus:border-amber-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-200 outline-none transition">
              <option value="">Select a service</option>
              <option value="private-tasting">Private Tasting</option>
              <option value="corporate-event">Corporate Event</option>
              <option value="wine-education">Wine Education Course</option>
              <option value="cellar-consulting">Cellar Consulting</option>
              <option value="other">Something else</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-stone-700 mb-1">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-stone-300 px-4 py-3 text-stone-800 focus:border-amber-500 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-amber-200 outline-none transition" placeholder="Tell me about your event, group size, and any preferences..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="bg-amber-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-amber-700 transition-colors w-full">Send Message</button>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-stone-100 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">Quick Details</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
            <div>
              <p class="text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Location</p>
              <p class="text-stone-800">Redwood City, CA — serving the entire Bay Area</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Availability</p>
              <p class="text-stone-800">Evenings & weekends for private events. Weekday availability for corporate bookings.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Group Size</p>
              <p class="text-stone-800">Intimate tastings (2–8 guests) to corporate events (up to 50 attendees).</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider text-xs mb-1">Lead Time</p>
              <p class="text-stone-800">2 weeks recommended for private tastings, 4+ weeks for corporate events.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">Not sure where to start?</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Browse my services to find the right fit, or explore the educational articles to get a taste of my approach.</p>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <a href="/services/private-tastings" class="text-amber-700 text-sm font-medium hover:text-amber-800 flex items-center gap-1">→ Private Tastings</a>
            <a href="/services/corporate-events" class="text-amber-700 text-sm font-medium hover:text-amber-800 flex items-center gap-1">→ Corporate Events</a>
            <a href="/learn/how-to-choose-wine" class="text-amber-700 text-sm font-medium hover:text-amber-800 flex items-center gap-1">→ How to Choose Wine</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
